commit 79ffe3fbb5b252b4a3b959deaf132f44a18453f8
Author: jrfnl <jrfnl@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Sat Mar 16 18:47:17 2019 +0100

    Generic/ArbitraryParenthesesSpacing: minor clean up
    
