    Support property-level extending for array properties

commit c961b32cf1edfccabaf04a9adf98cbb22e6e5094
Author: jrfnl <jrfnl@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Tue Oct 17 10:40:04 2017 +0200

    :sparkles: New Generic.VersionControl.GitMergeConflict sniff
    
    New sniff to detect merge conflict artefacts left in files.
    
    The sniff will throw errors independently for detected:
    * Merge conflict opening boundary.
    * Merge conflict delimiters `=======`.
    * Merge conflict closing boundary.
    
    The sniff walks the complete file in one go.
    
    The sniff takes the following special situations into account:
    * Detection after the tokenizer breaks down when unresolved merge conflicts are encountered.
    * Detection within inline HTML.
    * Detection within comments (all types).
    * Detection within Heredoc/nowdoc structures.
    * And combinations of the above.
    
    Includes extensive unit tests.

