    Fixed bug #890 : Function call inside returned short array value can cause indentation error inside CASE statements
    
    The ScopeIndent sniffs now keeps track of where it has set various indents so they can be restored later on. In this case, the code thought it was restoring the indent but it had been set again since the return keyword had been processed.

