commit 4315292970fb1e48cf14b4a9012c6cf78f22df68
Author: Greg Sherwood <gsherwood@squiz.net>
Date:   Wed Feb 10 15:22:30 2016 +1100

    Changed the way filtering of the file list works so that custom filters can be used.
    
    The code does not currently support custom filters, but all the basics are there to get it going. There are also 3 new filter classes:
    - Filter: the main one PHPCS uses to filter using the existing feature set
    - ExactFilter: an abstract class to make writing custom filters easier
    - GitModified: a filter to only check files modified or added in a git repo (used as an example of ExactFilter)

