commit 2d5cff23428b1e70c4838e8d39c1866f49fc44f3
Author: Arnout Boks <arnoutboks@gmail.com>
Date:   Thu May 16 15:30:32 2013 +0200

    Let OperatorSpacingSniff also check whitespace around an inline if
    
    Without this commit OperatorSpacingSniff considers
    ```
    $a = $x?$y:$z;
    ```
    to be fine. With this commit it counts 4 errors on that line for
    the missing spaces around the '?' and the ':'.
    
    Also includes a fix for the JS tokenizer not converting T_COLON to
    T_INLINE_ELSE when used in an inline if expression.

